Hi Tom, thanks for the info. I'm new to this site and not sure what or where the Sterling Auction is located haha. Could you point me in the right direction ?

Josh,

You can click on the "Vintage Links" symbol towards the top of each Net54 page.  Then click on the "Auction Sites" link and the page will list several different auction site options.  

Click on "Sterling Sports Auctions" and you will be taken to their web site.  You will have to register (its free) before being able to bid on any of the items in the auction.  The auction is ran by a Net54 member (Lee). 

Hope that this helps!
